title: Half-time Speech for Actors
description:
Written by Jon Bershad
Starring: Dan Hodapp, Jonathan Marballi, Avery Monsen, James McCarthy, Jon Bershad, Zack Phillips, Kelly Hudson.

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, August 5, 2013.

Filmed by Tom Levin, Curtis Raye.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
